IT120

#Day 1
   • What is Networking?
      ◦ A group of computers connected to each other

   • The goal of Networking?
      ◦ To make a remote resource act like a local resource

   • Dumb Terminals (CRT Terminal)
      ◦ Used for input and output to command remote computers
   
   • Modems
      ◦ Enabled a terminal to connect to a remote mainframe

   • Terminal manufacturers
      ◦ created standards for one terminal to connect to any mainframe
         ▸ custom terminals needed to be created beforehand
   
   • Moving data
      ◦ OSI Seven Layer Process
